ghost: well we need safe haven. you see, as I explained before, I'm a 
maximal. my original altmode was a small barn owl. while in the academy at 
New Iacon, I met goth. he discovered my wish to obtain a stronger body and we 
started working on putting me in one. long story short, we had finished this 
body and had it suspended above me. it had been designed to trap a spark 
exposed close to it. we were working on a spark extractor when the extractor 
explodes. it sends goth through a wall, blows my body to shreds, sends my 
spark flying towards the shell and brings down the entire ironhide memorial 
repair wing. goth woke up under150lbs of rubble, i woke up in this body, and 
everyone else woke up real mad. we were shipped out within 5 solar hours.

--part1_18.18e6f139.297e43c5_boundary
